		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd like to make games using character graphics akin to the Aquarius.  I can't find the current rights holder to Aquarius so maybe a different character set is in order.
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.vdsteenoven.com/aquarius/">http://www.vdsteenoven.com/aquarius/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />The set used in LogoNES is donationware which is OK but is suited mostly to making full screen art.
<br />
<br />What character graphic sets have people seen?  What would be the ideal set?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
